                    <div class="title">
                        Alex Agile, inspiring your workflow
                    </div>
                    <div class="description">
                        To be Agile doesn’t only mean to do stand-up meetings every morning, to have retrospectives
                        every other week or to move cards in a Kanban board.
                        <br><br>
                        To be Agile is a mindset, the kind of one that empowers individuals to pursue happiness through
                        Agile values and teamwork. If you want to become a good Agilist the first thing you need to
                        learn is to forget about yourself. You don’t matter anymore, your team and your organization
                        should be the first of your priorities and you should be sure that, if you belong into a happy
                        team and a happy organization, you will be happy.
                    </div>
